{
  "stem": "8916.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It just, it faded out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because when I first got it, I-- I sucked it out with my mouth and washed it off.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it-- it remained on my arm all through the war, but it was very, very faint.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody checked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Konzentrationslager.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Jewish doctors that tattooed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In any case--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember it being much-- very painful.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- when I was-- so Schindler agreed to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--put my mother and me on a list and I eventually made it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it-- that-- that didn't go very smoothly either, because I'd already worked-- been working in this brush factory and when the Schindler company was being formed, by that time, it was obvious that it was-- it would be preferable to be in the sub camp at Schindler's company than to be in Plaszow with-- with Goth as a commandant.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow someone decided that I could not be allowed out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I'd already-- I already had-- the pretense was that I already had a job, and I couldn't be going to Schindler's company.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to see her off too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just to-- again, same as before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were forming this group, and she was going to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I almost decided that this is going-- I was going to stay in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow, I'm not certain, but I approached the commandant or the officer who was going to escort those people to the-- to Emalia, and I reported.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I told him that I was on the list and I am not allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
